*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Report ZCL_STATIC_METHOD_641
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
REPORT zcl_static_method_641.

CLASS zcl_demo DEFINITION.
  PUBLIC SECTION.
    DATA lv_iv TYPE i.
    METHODS m1.
    CLASS-METHODS show_sm IMPORTING cl_obj TYPE REF TO zcl_demo.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_demo IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD show_sm.

    IF cl_obj IS BOUND.
      WRITE :/ 'Instance Variable =', cl_obj->lv_iv.
    ELSE.
      WRITE :/ 'No Reference Passed'.
    ENDIF.

  ENDMETHOD.

  METHOD m1.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

START-OF-SELECTION.
  DATA(obj) = NEW zcl_demo( ).
  obj->lv_iv = 123 .
  obj->m1( ).
  zcl_demo=>show_sm( obj ).


