*  PUBLIC SECTION .
*    METHODS m1.
*    CLASS-METHODS : m2.
*ENDCLASS.
*
*CLASS class1 IMPLEMENTATION.
*  METHOD m1.
*
*    WRITE : / ' i am Instance Method'.
*  ENDMETHOD.
*  METHOD m2.
*   "  DATA(lo_obj1) = new class1( ).
*    WRITE : / ' i am static Method '.
*    lo_obj1->m1( ).
*  ENDMETHOD.
*ENDCLASS.
*CLASS class2 DEFINITION INHERITING FROM class1.
