*    CLASS-METHODS m2 .
**    METHODs m2 REDEFINITION.
*
*    ENDCLASS.
*CLASS class2 IMPLEMENTATION.
*  METHOD m3.
*    DATA(obj) = NEW class2( ).
*    obj->m1( ).
*    obj->m2( ).
*  ENDMETHOD.
*ENDCLASS.
